headline.print_headline: Biggio Barely Misses Cut, Morris Left Out of Hall
headline.main: Biggio Barely Misses Cut, Morris Left Out of Hall

lead_paragraph: Craig Biggio barely came up short, so he'll be back next year. Jack Morris' outing is over, and he went the distance again.
